{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/optimize-blog-performance","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>HTML / CSS / JS / Photos 都是未压缩状态</li>\n<li>部分静态资源没有设置缓存</li>\n<li>CSS 出现阻塞，即首页出现空白的情况</li>\n</ul>\n<p>暂时只解决了第一个问题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>修改一下 <code class=\"language-text\">Travis CI</code> 的部署脚本 <code class=\"language-text\">.travis.yml</code> 即可实现自动压缩（利用 <code class=\"language-text\">gulpjs</code>）：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">install:\n- <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> hexo-cli gulp -g\n- <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span>\n\nscript:\n- hexo clean\n- hexo g\n- gulp\n- hexo d</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>查看 <a href=\"https://github.com/coderfe/blog/blob/master/gulpfile.js\"><code class=\"language-text\">gulpfile.js</code></a> 配置</p>\n<ul>\n<li>优化之后，加载速度明显提升了。剩下的几个问题还得研究一下</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"","frontmatter":{"path":"/optimize-blog-performance","date":"May 07, 2016","title":"优化博客性能","tldr":"今天发现博客首页的加载速度比较感人，于是就用 Google 出品的 Pagespeed Insights 检测了一下，发现了不少问题，而且这些问题都严重拖慢了加载时间。","tags":["性能优化"]},"timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"利用 TravisCI 自动部署 Hexo blog","path":"/automatic-deploy-hexo-blog-with-travis-ci"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Gulp and Browser-sync","path":"/use-browser-sync-with-gulp"}},"relatedPosts":[{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Ajax学习笔记","path":"/ajax"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"一些我自己常用的优质Apps","path":"/my-favorite-apps"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/front-end-performance-optimization-tips","tags":["性能优化"],"title":"前端性能优化"}}}]}}}